---
import HomepageLayout from '../layouts/HomepageLayout.astro';
---
<HomepageLayout title="Contact · HAS Design" activeNav="contact">
  <main class="prose-page">
    <article class="prose-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Get involved</p>
      <h1 class="prose-h1">Contact</h1>
      <div class="prose-body">
        <p>HAS-D is being built in public. That means the framework gets sharper through three kinds of input from the people working on the ground. Feedback: reactions to the premises, what's missing from v1.0, where the framing falls short. Testing: stories from real products, where the triad held, where it broke, what you learned applying it. Contributing: prior art HAS-D should be citing, phenomena worth naming, concepts that need sharpening. If you've got any of it, send it.</p>
      </div>

      <form class="contact-form" id="contact-form">
        <label class="contact-field">
          <span class="contact-label">Subject</span>
          <input type="text" id="cf-subject" name="subject" autocomplete="off" required />
        </label>
        <label class="contact-field">
          <span class="contact-label">Message</span>
          <textarea id="cf-message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
        </label>
        <label class="contact-field">
          <span class="contact-label">Reply email</span>
          <input type="email" id="cf-reply" name="reply" autocomplete="email" required />
        </label>
        <button type="submit" class="contact-send">Send</button>
      </form>
    </article>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var form = document.getElementById('contact-form');
      if (!form) return;
      form.addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        var subject = document.getElementById('cf-subject').value;
        var message = document.getElementById('cf-message').value;
        var reply = document.getElementById('cf-reply').value;
        var body = message + '\n\nReply to: ' + reply;
        var url = 'mailto:chadbercea@gmail.com'
          + '?subject=' + encodeURIComponent(subject)
          + '&body=' + encodeURIComponent(body);
        window.location.href = url;
      });
    })();
  </script>
</HomepageLayout>
